ent } from ‘@angular/core’;</p>\n<p>@Component({\nselector: ‘data-binding’,\ntemplate: <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div&gt;\n                 &lt;h1 [innerText]=&quot;myTitle&quot;&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;\n               &lt;/div&gt;</code>\n})\nexport class DataBindingComponent {\nmyTitle: string = ‘Hello, World’;\n}</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">## String Interpolation\n\njs```\nimport { Component } from &#39;@angular/core&#39;;\n\n@Component({\n    selector: &#39;string-interpolation&#39;,\n    template: `&lt;div&gt;\n                 &lt;h1&gt;{{ myTitle }}&lt;/h1&gt;\n               &lt;/div&gt;`\n})\nexport class StringInterpolationComponent {\n    myTitle: string = &#39;Hello, World&#39;;\n}</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2>Event Binding</h2>\n<p>js`<code class=\"language-text\"></code>\nimport { Component } from ‘@angular/core’;</p>\n<p>@Component({\nselector: ‘event-handling’,\ntemplate: <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div&gt;\n                 &lt;button (click)=&quot;handleClick()&quot;&gt;Press This Button!&lt;/button&gt;\n               &lt;/div&gt;</code>\n})\nexport class EventHandlingComponent {\nhandleClick(){\nconsole.log(‘the event has been handled!’)\n}\n}</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">## Two-Way Binding\n\njs```\nimport { Component } from &#39;@angular/core&#39;;\n\n@Component({\n    selector: &#39;two-way-binding&#39;,\n    template: `&lt;div&gt;\n                 &lt;input [(ngModel)]=&quot;name&quot;/&gt;\n               &lt;/div&gt;`\n})\nexport class TwoWayBindingComponent {\n    name: string = &#39;John Potts&#39;;\n}</code></pre>\n      </div>","excerpt":"In the Angular framework, components are set up with a template (view) Data Binding js` \nimport { Component } from ‘@angular/core…","fields":{"slug":"/2019-09-13-data-binding-in-angular/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"The Difference Between String I